    "body": "As a temporary fix, to avoid editing the `init.nu` directly, you can update your `env.nu` with the following:\r\n\r\n```shell\r\nstarship init nu\r\n| str replace --string 'PROMPT_COMMAND = {' 'PROMPT_COMMAND = { ||'\r\n| str replace --string 'PROMPT_COMMAND_RIGHT = {' 'PROMPT_COMMAND_RIGHT = { ||'\r\n| save -f ~/.cache/starship/init.nu\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis replaces the string returned from `starship init nu` to account for the latest changes.",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
