    "updated_at": "2023-04-10T21:50:55Z",
    "body": "If you're using nix you can also use an overlay to grab a revision of `starship` that has the fix. Here's one for the latest passing build:\r\n\r\n```nix\r\n    starship = prev.starship.overrideAttrs (oldAttrs: rec {\r\n      src = pkgs.fetchFromGitHub {\r\n        owner = \"starship\";\r\n        repo = \"starship\";\r\n        rev = \"07d9bb1691cf42c354a4feb3affd977b97e5b937\";\r\n        sha256 = \"sha256-jDvtUwPtBuQOXvecE8jPSIT2hsov6DybpeTjk3dH6Bc=\";\r\n      };\r\n      cargoDeps = oldAttrs.cargoDeps.overrideAttrs (prev.lib.const {\r\n        inherit src;\r\n        name = \"starship-07d9bb1691cf42c354a4feb3affd977b97e5b937-vendor.tar.gz\";\r\n        outputHash = \"sha256-jf+lb9rZTjdqRLpC+hN8M/+DgNMCoLCmb4CyqjYbvtM=\";\r\n      });\r\n    });\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\nPretty handy because the `nix` + `nushell` + `starship` combo can be pretty unstable.",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
