    "created_at": "2023-04-11T00:08:42Z",
    "updated_at": "2023-04-11T00:08:42Z",
    "body": "As an alternative, you can also [patch](https://github.com/srid/nixos-config/blob/e05b16124853ded2ab45f8b320e79f50b8e5b781/nixos/nix.nix#L12-L21) the existing release in Nix:\r\n\r\n```nix\r\n      starship = super.starship.overrideDerivation (oa: {\r\n        patches = (oa.patches or [ ]) ++ [\r\n          (builtins.fetchurl {\r\n            name = \"nushell.patch\";\r\n            url = \"https://github.com/starship/starship/commit/041a51835371d3738cc7b597b4a506a5dc4341c9.diff\";\r\n            sha256 = \"sha256:0az1jjb24mngzybgv7kavdj1bhfdm0cqnci3gz6zkgpaxqvw7vnz\";\r\n          })\r\n        ];\r\n      })\r\n```",
